Class Encounter

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompositeElement, IElement, IResource, ISupportsUndeclaredExtensions

    public class Encounter
extends BaseResource
implements IResource
    HAPI/FHIR Encounter Resource (An interaction during which services are provided to the patient)

    Definition: An interaction between a patient and healthcare provider(s) for the purpose of providing healthcare service(s) or assessing the health status of a patient.

    Requirements:

    Profile Definition: http://hl7.org/fhir/profiles/Encounter
